title: Coffee and walnut cake traybake
ingredients: ['For the cake', '225g butter or margarine, softened', '225g soft brown sugar', '4 eggs, lightly beaten', '2 tablespoons milk', '2 tablespoons coffee extract', '275g self raising flour', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '85g walnuts', 'For the icing', '75g unsalted butter, at room temperature', '225g icing sugar', '2 teaspoons milk', '2 teaspoons coffee extract', 'walnut halves, to decorate']
